#. Tag: title
#: datebar.docbook:9
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Datebar"
msgstr "Datumska vrstica"

#. Tag: para
#: datebar.docbook:11
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"At the bottom of the &kphotoalbum; main window, you will find the data bar "
"(see <xref linkend=\"fig-datebar\"/>). As the name indicates it shows date "
"statistics over the images in your database."
msgstr ""
"Na dnu glavnega okna &kphotoalbum; boste našli podatkovno vrstico (glejte "
"<xref linkend=\"fig-datebar\"/>). Kot že ime pove, prikazuje datumsko "
"statistiko nad slikami v vaši bazi podatkov."

#. Tag: title
#: datebar.docbook:16
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Date Bar"
msgstr "Datumska vrstica"

#. Tag: para
#: datebar.docbook:24
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The individual bars indicates how many images are within the given period. "
"In the figure above you may see that I have 261 images from January 2005. "
"The bars encode two information, namely how many images that have an exact "
"date within the given period, and how many have an overlap with the given "
"period. A picture which has a date that says 2005 will thus count as an "
"overlap for all the month of 2005, while an image from Jan 24th 2005 will "
"count as an exact date for January 2005. Exact matches are displayed with "
"green, while inexact matches are displayed in yellow. Thus in December 2004 "
"I have 86 images with exact count, and 61 with overlap count. (I know the "
"counts by hovering the mouse over the given range, since this displays the "
"counts in the status bar)."
msgstr ""
"Posamezne vrstice kažejo, koliko slik je v danem obdobju. Na zgornji sliki "
"lahko vidite, da imam 261 slik iz januarja 2005. Vrstici kodirata dve "
"informaciji, in sicer koliko slik ima točen datum znotraj danega obdobja in "
"koliko se jih prekriva z danim obdobjem. Slika z datumom 2005 bo tako štela "
"kot prekrivanje za ves mesec 2005, medtem ko bo slika od 24. januarja 2005 "
"štela kot natančen datum za januar 2005. Natančna ujemanja so prikazana z "
"zeleno, nenatančna pa prikazano rumeno. Tako imam decembra 2004 86 slik z "
"natančnim številom in 61 s številom prekrivanj. (Števce poznam tako, da se z "
"miško pomaknem nad dano območje, saj to prikaže štetje v statusni vrstici)."

#. Tag: para
#: datebar.docbook:36
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The date bar offers you a number of different granularities, where each bar "
"displays a different time range. The range are years, month, weeks, days, "
"hours, and 10 minutes. <xref linkend=\"fig-datebar-for-minutes\"/> shows you "
"part of my database where each bar shows only 10 minutes."
msgstr ""
"Datumska vrstica vam ponuja številne različne razdrobljenosti, kjer vsaka "
"vrstica prikazuje drugačen časovni obseg. Razpon je leta, mesec, tedni, "
"dnevi, ure in 10 minut. <xref linkend=\"fig-datebar-for-minutes\"/> vam "
"pokaže del moje baze podatkov, kjer vsaka vrstica prikazuje samo 10 minut."

#. Tag: title
#: datebar.docbook:43
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Date Bar Showing 10 Minutes Intervals"
msgstr "Datumska vrstica prikazuje 10-minutne intervale"

#. Tag: para
#: datebar.docbook:51
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The date bar is interactive in two ways, first you may navigate the "
"thumbnail view from the database - selecting a date will scroll the "
"thumbnail view so the first image from that date is displayed. Second, when "
"you navigate around in the thumbnail view, the date bar will update to "
"display the date of the images currently displayed."
msgstr ""
"Datumska vrstica je interaktivna na dva načina, najprej se lahko pomikate po "
"pogledu sličic iz baze podatkov – z izbiro datuma se bo pogled pomikal po "
"sličicah, tako da se prikaže prva slika od tega datuma. Drugič, ko se "
"premikate v pogledu sličic, se bo datumska vrstica posodobila in prikazala "
"datum trenutno prikazanih slik."

#. Tag: para
#: datebar.docbook:57
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You may also drag out a range in the data bar. You do so by pressing and "
"dragging the mouse in the ruler part of the date bar, i.e. on the time "
"stamps. When you select a range, the thumbnail viewer will display only "
"images from that range. You cancel a selection by pressing the cancel button "
"at the left side of the datebar."
msgstr ""
"Lahko tudi povlečete obseg v podatkovni vrstici. To storite tako, da z miško "
"pritisnete in povlečete v ravnilni del datumske vrstice, torej na časovne "
"žige. Ko izberete obseg, bo pregledovalnik sličic prikazal samo slike iz "
"tega obsega. Izbiro prekličete s pritiskom na gumb za preklic na levi strani "
"datumske vrstice."
